PrecisEnactment of the INSURANCE COMPANIES ASSESSED EXPENSES RECOVERY REGULATIONS which enable the Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions to reimburse insurance companies, on a pro rata basis, for assessed expenses in cases where the proceeds from the liquidation of a failed insurance company exceed a certain threshold.

precis:
Enactment of the INSURANCE COMPANIES ASSESSED EXPENSES RECOVERY REGULATIONS
which enable the Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions to
reimburse insurance companies, on a pro rata basis, for assessed expenses
in cases where the proceeds from the liquidation of a failed insurance
company exceed a certain threshold.
